summary: Stamus has came down for the heavens in the form of dragon born to stop Alduins evil plans.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds Stamus to the game. He is a very big, and very fast god. 
================================NOTES=============================
-He isn\'t very overpowered
-He is the size of a giant
-He has a large amount of stamina for all of that speed of his
-He his half dark elf and half nord
-He hates mondays and alduin
-He loves long walks on the beach and romantic sunsets 
-He can breathe underwater
++++++++++++++++++++++++++INSTALLATION++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Put the stamusproject.esp file into your data folder located in your skyrim directory
________________________UNINSTALLATION__________________________
Delete the stamusproject.esp file
